<pb ed="W" xml:id="W07.0059b.0061a" n="0061a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">錄文二</cb:mulu><head>〔錄文二〕</head>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a02"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a03"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>金剛五禮<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061001" n="0061001"/></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a04"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a05"/><p xml:id="pW07p0061a0501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061002" n="0061002"/>禮，清淨真如，無去無來，不生不滅，
<lb ed="W" n="0061a06"/>寂<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061003" n="0061003"/>然常住，坦<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061004" n="0061004"/>矣<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061005" n="0061005"/>恒安，千佛共遵<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061006" n="0061006"/>，十方同敬，恒
<lb ed="W" n="0061a07"/>沙功德，非色非心<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061007" n="0061007"/>，南無清淨法身毗盧遮那佛。</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a08"/><p xml:id="pW07p0061a0801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬禮，毗盧遮那，千葉蓮花，四智珍寶，
<lb ed="W" n="0061a09"/>德山無極，願海無邊，積行三祇，累功十地，光<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061008" n="0061008"/>充<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061009" n="0061009"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a10"/>法界，體滿虛空，南無圓滿報身盧舍那佛。</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a11"/><p xml:id="pW07p0061a1101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬禮，如來生地，雪山之<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061010" n="0061010"/>北，香山之東，
<lb ed="W" n="0061a12"/>城號加維，姓<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061011" n="0061011"/>釋迦氏<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061012" n="0061012"/>，父名淨飯，母曰<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061013" n="0061013"/>摩耶，十
<lb ed="W" n="0061a13"/>九出家，三十<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061014" n="0061014"/>成道，南無千百億化身釋<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061015" n="0061015"/>迦牟尼佛。</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0061a14"/><p xml:id="pW07p0061a1401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬禮，甚深微妙，金剛般若<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0061016" n="0061016"/>，不可思議<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062001" n="0062001"/>，
<pb ed="W" xml:id="W07.0059b.0062a" n="0062a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0062a01"/>生諸佛身，滅凡夫罪，無人無我，聲空色空，苦惱
<lb ed="W" n="0062a02"/>蓋纏，因此<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062002" n="0062002"/>永寂<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062003" n="0062003"/>，南無般<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062004" n="0062004"/>若波羅蜜多甚<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062005" n="0062005"/>深法藏。</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0062a03"/><p xml:id="pW07p0062a0301" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬禮，舍衛城南<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062006" n="0062006"/>，須達園中，祇陀林下，
<lb ed="W" n="0062a04"/>如來精舍<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062007" n="0062007"/>，聖眾禪房，於彼<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062008" n="0062008"/>伽藍<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062009" n="0062009"/>，說斯<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062010" n="0062010"/>般若，我
<lb ed="W" n="0062a05"/>今恭<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062011" n="0062011"/>敬，追<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062012" n="0062012"/>念世尊，南無般<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062013" n="0062013"/>若波羅蜜多甚<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062014" n="0062014"/>深法
<lb ed="W" n="0062a06"/>藏<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062015" n="0062015"/>。</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0062a07"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0062a08"/><p xml:id="pW07p0062a0801">〔錄文完〕</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="W" n="0062a09"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0062a10"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pW07p0062a1001" rend="margin-left:8em">（方廣錩修訂終審）</p></cb:div>
</body>
